OL,3,C'No routes' for storm compensation
OL,5,FThere are "no routes" for Northern
OL,6,FIreland Electricity Networks to make
OL,7,Fcompensation payments to customers who
OL,8,Flost power during Storm Eowyn, a
OL,9,Fworking group has said.
OL,11,FAlmost 326,000 homes and businesses
OL,12,Flost power as a result of the storm in
OL,13,FJanuary.
OL,15,FWidespread damage was mainly caused by
OL,16,Ftrees striking overhead electricity
OL,17,Fwires. More than 90% of NIE's primary
OL,18,Fsubstations across Northern Ireland
OL,19,Fexperienced wind gusts in excess of
OL,20,F90mph.
