OL,3,C'No routes' for storm compensation
OL,5,FA working group involving the
OL,6,FDepartment for the Economy, NIE
OL,7,FNetworks and the Utility Regulator was
OL,8,Fset up to consider compensation for
OL,9,Fcustomers most affected by power
OL,10,Foutages.
OL,12,FIt was established at the request of
OL,13,Fthe Stormont Executive to consider
OL,14,Foptions where payments would be
OL,15,Frecovered through customer electricity
OL,16,Fbills.
OL,18,FHowever the group has concluded there
OL,19,Fis "currently no existing route to
OL,20,Fmake payments to customers".
