OL,3,C'No routes' for storm compensation
OL,5,FA Department for the Economy
OL,6,Fspokesperson said NIE Networks has
OL,7,Fapplied a severe weather exemption,
OL,8,Fwhich is provided for in legislation
OL,9,Funder which customers would usually
OL,10,Fapply for compensation if they have
OL,11,Fbeen off electricity supply.
OL,13,F"The working group concluded that any
OL,14,Fother options involving recovery of
OL,15,Fpayments from network charges would
OL,16,Frequire legal or regulatory
OL,17,Fmodifications which cannot be applied
OL,18,Fretrospectively for those customers
OL,19,Fimpacted by Storm Eowyn," they said.
